description:
===================================================================================
Blue Bloods follows the lives of the NYPD's First Family of Law Enforcement: the Reagans. Frank| the Police Comissioner and son of former PC Henry Reagan| must
balance his duties of running the largest police force in the world and being his kids' boss. His daughter Erin is an Assistant District Attorney| son Danny is a
senior detective and fellow Marine Veteran| and new Harvard Law grad turned cop| Jamie all swirl through this family drama and passionately defend their city from
harm. The Irish-American family is deeply rooted in their patriotism| passion| and love of family.
